data.description: Have you been wanting to get into Harbor Lakes? Seller says price it to sell. Get this one before it's gone at this price!                                                                                                        Located in the Whitewater School District on a quiet cul-de-sac street. This home has space for everyone from a full in law suite on lower terrace to 4 spacious bedrooms upstairs. The entrance opens to a spacious 2 story foyer. On the main floor there is a large office or additional den area, a formal dining room, spacious family room with built in shelves and fireplace,  open kitchen with upgraded appliances, a breakfast area, 2 pantries and half bath. Upstairs there are dual vanities in master bath and walk in closet, linen closets in master and hallway, bonus room/bedroom, lower level offers finished studio complete with kitchen, living room, bedroom, full bath,closet, storage room, and patio area. In law suite also includes washer, dryer, refrigerator, and new carpet. This home also features a Rinnai Tankless hot water heater and newer HVAC unitse  Established landscaping including an amazing fig tree and koi pond/water feature in back yard.  Neighborhood amenities include swimming, tennis, playground.  Close to shopping, restaurants, airport, Pinewood Studios. Minutes from Lake Horton.  Plenty of space at price per square footage that that is well under other comparable properties in the Whitewater district. Virtual Tour Available on YouTube.  Type 135 Marina  Ct, Fayetteville in YouTube Search Bar. 2020-05-08
